longBusinessSummary: INTERSHOP Communications Aktiengesellschaft provides omnichannel commerce solutions worldwide. It operates in two segments, Software and Cloud, and Service. The company offers packaged software for Internet sales, as well as acts as a business process outsourcing provider. In addition, it provides commerce platform for commerce management, experience management, product information management, and order management. Further, the company provides implementation, go-live support, and project management services; training services; and customer success and support services. It serves manufacturing, wholesale, retail, B2C, B2X, and B2B sectors. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Jena, Germany.
